DataSource.RecordSource: PARAMETERS @InvoiceNumber string 'INCCL125'; SELECT (MID([TaskCode],2,LEN([TaskCode])-1)) AS TaskCodes, Category, TaskDescription AS Description, CompletedDate AS Completed, IIF(IsNull(HoursSold),0,IIF(TaskCode='T002338', HoursSold*75, HoursSold * HourlyRate)) AS Amount, Customer, InvoiceNumber, BillerContact FROM (tblTasks INNER JOIN tblCustomers ON tblTasks.CustomerCode = tblCustomers.CustomerCode) INNER JOIN tblStaff ON tblTasks.PrimaryDeveloper = tblStaff.StaffCode WHERE InvoiceNumber = @InvoiceNumber order by Category, TaskCode

DataSource.RecordSource: PARAMETERS @MonDate datetime '',@Staff string ''; SELECT Q.Staff,Q.MonDate,Q.TaskCode,T.TaskDescription,C.LogId,DateValue(C.LogDate) as LogDate, C.Comment,C.AttachmentName,C.Author FROM (qryWeeklyTimesheet Q INNER JOIN tblTasks T ON Q.TaskCode = T.TaskCode) INNER JOIN tblCommunicationsLog C ON Q.TaskCode = C.TaskCode AND Q.Staff = C.Author AND C.LogDate >= Q.MonDate AND C.LogDate < DATEADD("d",7,Q.MonDate) WHERE Q.MonDate=@MonDate AND Q.Staff =@Staff

PARAMETERS @MonDate datetime '',@Staff string ''; SELECT Q.Staff,Q.MonDate, Q.TaskCode,T.TaskDescription, C.LogId,DateValue(C.LogDate) as LogDate, C.Comment,C.AttachmentName,C.Author FROM (qryWeeklyTimesheet Q INNER JOIN tblTasks T ON Q.TaskCode = T.TaskCode) INNER JOIN tblCommunicationsLog C ON Q.TaskCode = C.TaskCode AND Q.Staff = C.Author AND C.LogDate >= Q.MonDate AND C.LogDate < DATEADD("d",7,Q.MonDate) WHERE Q.MonDate = @MonDate AND Q.Staff = @Staff

PARAMETERS @MonDate datetime '',@Staff string ''; SELECT Q.Staff,Q.MonDate, Q.TaskCode,T.TaskDescription, Q.TotalDuration,Q.TotalBillableDuration, Format(TI.StartTime,"ddd") as DayOfTheWeek, DateValue(TI.StartTime) as DateOfTheWeek, IIF(Format(TI.StartTime,"ddd") = "Mon", Q.MonDuration, IIF(Format(TI.StartTime,"ddd") = "Tue", Q.TueDuration, IIF(Format(TI.StartTime,"ddd") = "Wed", Q.WedDuration, IIF(Format(TI.StartTime,"ddd") = "Thu", Q.ThuDuration, IIF(Format(TI.StartTime,"ddd") = "Fri", Q.FriDuration, IIF(Format(TI.StartTime,"ddd") = "Sat", Q.SatDuration,SunDuration)))))) AS DayDuration, Format(TI.StartTime,"HH:mm") as StartTime, Format(TI.EndTime,"HH:mm") as EndTime, DATEDIFF("s",TI.StartTime,TI.EndTime) / 3600 AS Duration FROM (qryWeeklyTimesheet Q INNER JOIN tblTasks T ON Q.TaskCode = T.TaskCode) INNER JOIN tblTimings TI ON Q.TaskCode = TI.TaskCode AND Q.Staff = TI.Staff AND TI.StartTime >= Q.MonDate AND TI.StartTime < DATEADD("d",7,Q.MonDate) WHERE Q.MonDate = @MonDate AND Q.Staff = @Staff ORDER BY TI.StartTime
